PACULA
v.
STATE of NC. No. 682P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006.

Richard S. Pacula, Pro Se.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 16th day of December 2005 by Appellee (Brunswick County) to Dismiss Appeal:
